999
01:10:53,541 --> 01:10:57,171
<i>Off they go.
Powell is off well. Bolt has work to do.</i>

1000
01:10:57,295 --> 01:10:59,585
<i>Powell is ahead of Bolt
and the rest of the field.</i>

