01:13:01,294 --> 01:13:04,964
<i>The fastest group of
sprinters that has ever taken the line</i>

1028
01:13:05,089 --> 01:13:06,379
<i>in a 100-meter olympic final.</i>

1029
01:13:06,507 --> 01:13:10,967
<i>God put me on this earth to run,
